0mother%20of%20two%20of%20his%20children.%20But%20in%20at%20least%20one%20instance%2C%20the%20person%20who%20answered%20the%20door%20at%20Zilis'%20house%20told%20the%20process%20server%20they%20didn't%20know%20Musk%2C%20the%20court%20documents%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20servers%20were%20unable%20to%20deliver%20the%20court%20documents%20to%20Musk%20personally%2C%20and%20were%20shooed%20away%20in%20several%20instances%2C%20including%20by%20security%20personnel%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETesla%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20X%2C%20and%20a%20police%20officer%20in%20Boca%20Chica.%20The%20servers%20said%20they%20left%20the%20papers%20with%20several%20secondary%20personnel%2C%20including%20security%20workers%20at%20X%2C%20Tesla%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESpaceX%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrimes%20'made%20more%20than%20reasonable%20efforts'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20court%20papers%2C%20Grimes%20said%20her%20process%20server%20handing%20her%20complaint%20to%20Musk's%20security%20at%20X%20was%20proof%20enough%20that%20she'd%20served%20her%20childrens'%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Melcher%2C%20a%20California%20family%20law%20attorney%20and%20partner%20at%20Walzer%20Melcher%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20three%20attempts%20to%20serve%20someone%20is%20typically%20sufficient%20under%20California%20law%20and%20that%20Grimes'%20team%20%26quot%3Bmade%20more%20than%20reasonable%20efforts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20substitute%20service%2C%20when%20papers%20are%20left%20with%20someone%20else%20at%20the%20person's%20home%20or%20business%2C%20is%20acceptable%20if%20reasonable%20attempts%20are%20made%20to%20serve%20them%20directly.%20The%20practice%20is%20especially%20relev