is%20at%20her%20home%20in%20Austin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%2010%20known%20living%20children%20who%20he%20has%20fathered%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spouse-married%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethree%20different%20women%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20his%20youngest%2C%20a%20one-year-old%20son%20named%20Techno%20Mechanicus%2C%20or%20Tau%2C%20who%20he%20fathered%20with%20Grimes%20and%20was%20born%20via%20a%20surrogate%20last%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrimes-custody-elon-musk-children-x-tesla-spacex-neuralink-headquarters-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699610401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654d902536d588dc55ce37ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrimes-custody-elon-musk-children-x-tesla-spacex-neuralink-headquarters-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Grimes%20tried%20to%20find%20Elon%20Musk%20at%20headquarters%20for%20X%2C%20Tesla%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20and%20Neuralink%2C%20among%20other%20locations%2C%20to%20serve%20him%20papers%20in%20their%20custody%20fight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gkay%40insider.com%20(Grace%20Kay%2CKelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrimes-custody-elon-musk-children-x-tesla-spacex-neuralink-headquarters-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Curious%20Case%20of%20Supreme%20Court's%20Denial%20of%20Bail%20to%20Manish%20Sisodia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F10151751%2FFnEB_zZaEAAAcQ4.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20days%20of%20prohibition%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20bootlegging%20mafia%20generated%20huge%20amounts%20of%20money%20in%20cash.%20The%20acquisition%20of%20cash%20had%20to%20be%20legitimised%20and%20the%20mafia%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20setting%20up%20laundromats%20or%20laundries%2C%20where%20customers%20normally%20pay%20their%20dues%20in%20cash.%20This%20financial%20innovation%20to%20whitewash%20money%20from%20illicit%20trade%20into%20legitimate%20business%20proceeds%20was%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9Cmoney%20laundering%E2%80%9D.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20truth%20universally%20acknowledged%20that%20illicit%20trades%20generate%20large%20amounts%20of%20cash%20and%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20of%20curbing%20illicit%20trade%20is%20to%20curb%20the%20outflow%20and%20utility%20of%20cash%20proceeds.%20The%20process%20of%20money%20laundering%20typically%20involves%20the%20principles%20of%20placement%2C%20layering%20and%20integration.%20Especially%20the%20illicit%20trade%20in%20arms%20and%20drugs%20%E2%80%93%20which%20generates%20huge%20cash%20profits%20%E2%80%93%20was%20sought%20to%20be%20curbed%20on%20an%20international%20scale%20with%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force%20in%201989.%20In%201990%2C%20the%20Political%20Declaration%20and%20Global%20Programme%20of%20Action%20was%20adopted%20and%20in%201998%2C%20the%20Political%20Declaration%20and%20Action%20Plan%20against%20Money%20Laundering%20was%20adopted.%20Following%20the%20adoption%20of%20these%20instruments%2C%20India%20enacted%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20in%202002.%20Implementation%20of%20the%20Act%20was%20left%20to%20the%20domain%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%2C%20a%20division%20of%20the%20finance%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20far%20from%20confining%20itself%20to%20the%20laundering%20of%20drugs%20and%20arms%20money%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20ended%20up%20diluting%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20Act%20by%20including%20a%20whole%20host%20of%20unconnected%20ordinary%20offences%20in%20the%20schedule%20to%20the%20PMLA%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpredicate%20offences%E2%80%9D.%20Crimes%20under%20the%20Copyright%20Act%2C%20pollution%20Acts%20and%20a%20whole%20host%20of%20economic%20offences%20including%20bribery%2C%20were%20jostled%20into%20an%20overbroad%20schedule.%20If%20money%20was%20earned%20from%20any%20of%20these%20offences%20and%20then%20sought%20to%20be%20legitimised%20by%20investing%20its%20proceeds%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20assets%2C%20those%20assets%20were%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98proceeds%20of%20crime%E2%80%99.%20The%20PMLA%20allowed%20the%20state%20to%20seize%20to%20punish%20those%20who%20sought%20to%20launder%20the%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrdinarily%2C%20the%20investigation%20of%20most%20crimes%20is%20done%20by%20the%20State%20Police%20Department%20as%20law%20and%20order%20is%20a%20state%20subject.%20State%20governments%20effectively%20decided%20which%20crimes%20were%20investigated%20and%20which%20were%20neglected.%20The%20Union%20government%20used%20to%20interfere%20in%20criminal%20investigations%20through%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%20However%2C%20the%20CBI%20legislation%20required%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20state%20to%20operate%20within%20its%20territory.%20When%20faced%20with%20overzealous%20central%20investigations%2C%20many%20states%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftelangana-government-withdraws-general-consent-to-cbi%5C%22%3Erefused%20permission%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20CBI%20to%20operate%20within%20their%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Investigatorial%E2%80%99%20vengeance%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%2C%20however%2C%20has%20no%20such%20limitation.%20And%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20particularly%20under%20the%20NDA%20government%2C%20it%20has%20become%20an%20institution%20of%20what%20one%20might%20term%2C%20investigatorial%20vengeance%20against%20politicians%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20and%20opposition-ruled%20states.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20ED%20recently%20summoned%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20son%20to%20Delhi%20and%20conducted%20searches%20at%20the%20premises%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20political%20adviser.%20In%20short%2C%20electoral%20deficiencies%20were%20remedied%20and%20electoral%20dominance%20was%20achieved%20by%20generous%20resort%20to%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Opposition%20politicians%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20earlier%20this%20year%20against%20the%20misuse%20of%20the%20ED.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fguidelines-exclusively-for-politicians-sc-turns-down-opposition-petition-on-agency-misuse%5C%22%3Erefused%20to%20entertain%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20petition%20and%20allowed%20the%20petition%20to%20be%20withdrawn%20while%20observing%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%9CCome%20back%20with%20a%20concrete%20case%2C%20where%20there%20has%20been%20a%20specific%20instance%20or%20instances%20of%20the%20agencies%20being%20used%20to%20selectively%20target%20leaders.%20On%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20law%20that%20we%20have%20laid%20down%2C%20we%20can%20evolve%20general%20principles%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20facts%20of%20the%20case.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20case%20came%20squarely%20before%20the%20court%20in%20Manish%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20bail%20application%20and%20in%20the%20opinion%20of%20this%20author%2C%20the%20judgment%20has%20failed%20the%20standards%20of%20fairness%20to%20which%20every%20accused%20is%20entitled%20and%20sets%20a%20dangerous%20prosecution-friendly%20precedent%20which%20may%20later%20come%20to%20haunt%20those%20who%20are%20in%20power%20today%20but%20may%20not%20be%20in%20the%20same%20position%20tomorrow.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanish-sisodia-bail-sc-denial-questions%5C%22%3ENo%20Bail%20to%20Sisodia%3A%20SC%20Ignored%20Basic%20Principles%2C%20Questions%20of%20Targeted%20Political%20Persecution%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhere%20are%20the%20%E2%80%9Cproceeds%20of%20crime%E2%80%9D%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBriefly%20stated%2C%20the%20prosecution%20case%20is%20that%20the%20liquor%20policy%20in%20Delhi%20was%20changed%20to%20give%20wholesale%20distributors%2012%25%20commission%20instead%20of%205%25%20and%20the%20estimated%20difference%20earned%20by%20the%20wholesalers%20was%20to%20the%20order%20of%20Rs%20585%20crore.%20About%20Rs%20100%20crore%20of%20this%20extra%20profit%20has%20been%20alleged%20to%20have%20been%20utilised%20to%20support%20the%20AAP%20campaign%20in%20the%20Goa%20elections.%20There%20appears%20to%20be%20no%20particular%2C%20specific%20money%20which%20is%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Manish%20Sisodia%20or%20under%20his%20direct%20control.%20There%20are%20thus%20no%20directly%20displayable%20%E2%80%9Cproceeds%20of%20crime.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20remembered%20that%20bribery%20is%20an%20offence%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%2C%201988%20and%20is%20a%20predicate%20offence%20under%20the%20PMLA.%20However%2C%20not%20every%20case%20of%20bribery%20is%20a%20case%20of%20money%20laundering%20%E2%80%93%20unless%20and%20until%20the%20money%20generated%20from%20the%20offence%20of%20bribery%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20converted%20into%20assets%20which%20could%20be%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%9CProceeds%20of%20Crime%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20such%20demonstrable%20proceeds%2C%20there%20would%20be%20no%20case%20of%20money%20laundering%20established%20over%20which%20the%20ED%20would%20have%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SC%20itself%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F14485072%2F%5C%22%3EVijay%20Madanlal%20Choudhary%20vs%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20matter%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Eillustrated%20how%20every%20commodity%20involved%20in%20a%20crime%20does%20not%20turn%20into%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20vehicle%20used%20in%20the%20commission%20of%20a%20scheduled%20offence%20may%20be%20attached%20as%20property%20in%20the%20concerned%20case%20(crime)%20but%20it%20may%20still%20not%20be%20within%20the%20meaning%20of%20%E2%80%9Cproceeds%20of%20crime%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20PMLA.%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20circumstances%2C%20it%20does%20reasonably%20appear%20that%20the%20ED%20was%20on%20a%20roving%20and%20fishing%20expedition%20to%20somehow%20connect%20the%20minister%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20liquor%20policy%20with%20the%20crime%20of%20money%20laundering%20and%20to%20possibly%20fix%20others%20higher%20up%20in%20the%20ministerial%20chain%20with%20the%20same%20offence.%20Two%20things%20need%20to%20be%20emphasised%20%E2%80%93%20the%20change%20in%20liquor%20policy%20was%20not%20the%20act%20of%20Sisodia%20alone.%20It%20was%20in%20fact%2C%20endorsed%20by%20a%20cabinet%20decision.%20The%20court%2C%20while%20dealing%20with%20the%20question%20of%20bail%2C%20has%20specifically%20kept%20aside%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20a%20cabinet%20decision%20can%20be%20made%20the%20subject%20matter%20of%20a%20criminal%20prosecution.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20has%20got%20over%20the%20inconvenient%20fact%20that%20there%20currently%20exists%20no%20proven%20money%20trail%20directly%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20Sisodia%20by%20saying%20that%20even%20if%20money%20was%20spent%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20in%20Goa%2C%20he%20exercised%20%E2%80%9Cpossessory%20domain%E2%80%9D%20over%20the%20money%20spent.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20problem%20with%20any%20case%20being%20filed%20by%20the%20ED%20is%20the%20extreme%20difficulty%20in%20securing%20bail.%20Section%2045%20of%20the%20PMLA%20requires%20that%20the%20court%20should%20be%20satisfied%20that%20the%20person%20is%20not%20guilty%20and%20is%20not%20likely%20to%20repeat%20the%20offence.%20Similar%20provisions%20in%20other%20Acts%20have%20been%20interpreted%20by%20the%20court%20to%20make%20the%20grant%20of%20bail%20almost%20impossible%20without%20concluding%20a%20full%20trial.%20It%20is%20also%20pertinent%20to%20state%20that%20very%20rarely%20has%20a%20PMLA%20case%20gone%20to%20trial%20and%20been%20concluded%20in%20a%20reasonable%20amount%20of%20time%2C%20thus%20when%20a%20man%20is%20arrested%20under%20the%20PMLA%20and%20no%20speedy%20trial%20is%20available%20and%20no%20bail%20pending%20trial%20is%20granted%2C%20the%20process%20itself%20is%20the%20punishment.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png-300x150.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png-1024x512.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png-800x400.png%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670931%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%20Photo%3A%20Pinakpani%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESelective%20application%20of%20harsh%20laws%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sisodia%20judgment%20is%20a%20rare%20lengthy%20judgment%20of%2041%20pages%20which%20denies%20bail%20to%20an%20accused.%20The%20only%20clear%20charge%20that%20the%20court%20has%20relied%20upon%20is%20a%20charge%20of%20causing%20loss%20to%20the%20public%20exchequer.%20Absent%20any%20element%20of%20personal%20aggrandisement%20or%20creation%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime%2C%20the%20PMLA%20case%20should%20not%20have%20been%20allowed%20to%20continue.%20Instead%2C%20the%20court%20has%20given%20the%20prosecution%20a%20further%20chance%20to%20prove%20its%20case%20and%20allowed%20Sisodia%20an%20opportunity%20to%20apply%20again%20for%20bail%20if%20the%20trial%20moves%20at%20a%20snail%E2%80%99s%20pace%20over%20the%20next%20three%20months.%20This%20judgment%20will%20have%20a%20precedential%20value%20that%20will%20bind%20all%20courts%20in%20India.%20The%20surprisingly%20thin%20logic%20of%20this%20judgment%20will%20end%20up%20denying%20the%20liberty%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20citizens%20other%20than%20Manish%20Sisodia%20who%20have%20also%20been%20caught%20in%20the%20Kafkaesque%20world%20of%20the%20PMLA.%20While%20hard%20cases%20are%20known%20to%20make%20bad%20law%2C%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20case%20is%20that%20of%20a%20bad%20law%2C%20being%20made%20harder%20by%20a%20harsher%20interpretation%20of%20harsh%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomeone%20has%20rightly%20said%20that%20the%20essence%20of%20tyranny%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20make%20a%20harsh%20law%20and%20use%20it%20selectively%20against%20your%20opponents.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20courts%20fail%20to%20see%20through%20this%20game%2C%20they%20fail%20to%20perform%20their%20constitutional%20duty%20to%20protect%20the%20lives%20and%20liberties%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699610101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F10151751%2FFnEB_zZaEAAAcQ4.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcurious-case-denial-bail-manish-sisodia-supreme-court%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20rightly%20said%20that%20the%20essence%20of%20tyranny%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20make%20a%