ted%20by%20former%20Infosys%20CFO%20Mohandas%20Pai.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20example%20of%20how%20other%20nations%20have%20enhanced%20their%20productivity%2C%20Mr%20Murthy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20exactly%20what%20the%20Germans%20and%20Japanese%20did%20after%20the%20Second%20World%20War...they%20made%20sure%20that%20every%20German%20worked%20extra%20hours%20for%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20JSW%20Chairman%20Sajjan%20Jindal%20had%20also%20supported%20Mr%20Murthy's%20remarks.%20%26quot%3BI%20wholeheartedly%20endorse%20Mr%20Narayana%20Murthy's%20statement.%20It's%20not%20about%20burnout%2C%20it's%20about%20dedication.%20We%20have%20to%20make%20India%20an%20economic%20superpower%20that%20we%20can%20all%20be%20proud%20of%20in%20India%202047%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jindal%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgreeing%20with%20Narayana%20Murthy%2C%20Ola%20CEO%20Bhavish%20Aggarwal%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTotally%20agree%20with%20Mr%20Murthy's%20views.%20It's%20not%20our%20moment%20to%20work%20less%20and%20entertain%20ourselves.%20Rather%20it's%20our%20moment%20to%20go%20all%20in%20and%20build%20in%201%20generation%20what%20other%20countries%20have%20built%20over%20many%20generations!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699602060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-01%2Fmanish-tewari_650x400_81452428702.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-infosys-must-become-a-norm-congress-leader-backs-70-hour-work-week-advice-4563362%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Manish%20Tewari%20today%20joined%20the%20ongoing%20debate%20over%20Infosys%20chairman%20Narayana%20Murthy's%2070-hour%20work%20week%20advice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-infosys-must-become-a-norm-congress-leader-backs-70-hour-work-week-advice-4563362%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-infosys-must-become-a-norm-congress-leader-backs-70-hour-work-week-advice-4563362%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-infosys-must-become-a-norm-congress-leader-backs-70-hour-work-week-advice-4563362%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20needs%208%25-8.5%25%20growth%20to%20create%20enough%20jobs%2C%20says%20Raghuram%20Rajan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699601933000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-12%2F02%2Ffull%2F1669981186-601.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-needs-8-8-5-growth-to-create-enough-jobs-says-raghuram-rajan-123111000409_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20India's%20expansion%20has%20outpaced%20that%20of%20other%20major%20economies%2C%20the%20country%20isn't%20creating%20enough%20jobs%20for%20the%20millions%20of%20people%20joining%20the%20workforce%20every%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-needs-8-8-5-growth-to-create-enough-jobs-says-raghuram-rajan-123111000409_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-needs-8-8-5-growth-to-create-enough-jobs-says-raghuram-rajan-123111000409_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-needs-8-8-5-growth-to-create-enough-jobs-says-raghuram-rajan-123111000409_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fertiliser%20Shortage%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Despite%20Abundant%20Stock.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFarmers%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20forced%20to%20wait%20in%20long%20queues%20to%20buy%20fertiliser%20after%20a%20full%20stock%20became%20unfit%20for%20sale%20due%20to%20negligence%20of%20district%20officials.%20Weeks%20after%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20was%20imposed%2C%20officials%20failed%20to%20erase%20or%20cover%20up%20pictures%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20fertiliser%20packets%20and%20now%20they%20can't%20be%20legally%20distributed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%2C%20which%20was%20implemented%20in%20the%20state%20on%20October%209%2C%20dictates%20that%20state-distributed%20merchandise%20can%20not%20have%20photographs%20or%20symbols%20of%20any%20political%20party%20or%20leader.%20Upon%20receiving%20a%20complaint%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20ordered%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Chemicals%20and%20Fertilizers%20to%20remove%20PM's%20photo%20from%20the%20sacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20no%20end%20to%20the%20shortage%20in%20sight%20and%20fearing%20delay%20in%20Rabi%20sowing%20season%2C%20anxious%20farmers%20are%20buying%20bags%20of%20fertiliser%20at%20over-inflated%20prices.%20Hari%20Singh%20Saini%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Entkhedi%20village%20near%20Bhopal%2C%20has%20managed%20to%20purchase%20only%2015%20bags%20of%20DAP%2C%20a%20phosphate-based%20fertiliser%2C%20for%20his%2012-acre%20land.%20%26quot%3BOur%20expenses%20have%20gone%20up%20by%2020%25.%20It%20has%20become%20very%20difficult.%20We%20will%20end%20up%20with%20a%20lower%20yield%2C%20earning%20close%20to%20nothing%20from%20this%20crop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bhopal's%20Nipaniya%20Jat%20village%2C%20one%20farmer%20is%20being%20given%20one%20sack%20of%20DAP%20and%20two%20sacks%20of%20Urea.%20Even%20though%20fertiliser%20with%20the%20revised%20packaging%20is%20available%2C%20farmers%20complain%20of%20rising%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELokendra%20Jat%2C%20a%20local%20farmer%20says%20a%20bag%20of%20urea%20which%20used%20to%20be%2050%20kg%20bag%20is%20now%20repackaged%20into%2045%20kg%20bags%20while%20the%20price%20remains%20the%20same.%20%26quot%3BA%20bag%20of%20DAP%20used%20to%20cost%20Rs%201%2C200%20but%20its%20now%20Rs%201%2C365.%20The%20price%20of%20granular%20fertiliser%20has%20also%20gone%20up%20from%20Rs%20310%20to%20Rs%20468.%20This%20will%20impact%20the%20yield%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Rewa%20and%20Dewas%20are%20not%20facing%20a%20shortage%20due%20to%20incorrect%20packaging%2C%20farmers%20complain%20of%20waiting%20in%20queues%20for%20over%20five%20hours%20and%20forced%20to%20make%20two%20to%20three%20trips%20to%20get%20fertiliser%20just%20a%20few%20bags%20of%20fertiliser.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20Mandsaur%2C%20the%20revision%20of%20packaging%20has%20led%20to%20a%20confusion%20with%20even%20the%20correctly%20packaged%20fertiliser%20being%20distributed%20at%20slow%20rates.%20Ramesh%20Masare%2C%20a%20local%20Tehsildar%20told%20NDTV%2C%20that%20the%20long%20queues%20are%20caused%20by%20farmers%20from%20other%20districts%20coming%20there%20to%20buy%20fertiliser%20but%20denied%20any%20news%20of%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20both%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20intensify%20their%20poll%20campaigns%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20issue%20also%20came%20up%20in%20the%20speeches%20of%20party%20leaders%20and%20Union%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20fertiliser%20shortage%20in%20the%20state%20and%20denied%20any%20long%20queues%20outside%20distribution%20centres.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20in%20power%2C%20there%20has%20never%20been%20any%20shortage%20of%20urea%20or%20fertiliser%20for%20the%20farmers.%20Delivery%20has%20been%20done%20on%20time%20to%20farmers%20without%20standing%20in%20queue.%20Even%20today%2C%20there%20is%20no%20problem%20in%20fertiliser%20distribution%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20while%20addressing%20a%20rally%20in%20MP%20accused%20BJP%20of%20%26quot%3Bcheating%20farmers%20and%20not%20doing%20anything%20for%20them%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20officials%20about%206.42%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20urea%20arrived%20in%20the%20state%2C%202.86%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20has%20been%20sold%20with%203.56%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20leftover.%20Out%20of%20the%20total%204.31%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20DAP%2C%202.03%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20has%20been%20distributed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699601760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fikdm59n_madhya-pradesh-fertiliser_625x300_10_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffertiliser-shortage-in-madhya-pradesh-despite-abundant-stock-heres-why-4563396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farmers%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20forced%20to%20wait%20in%20long%20queues%20to%20buy%20fertiliser%20after%20a%20full%20stock%20became%20unfit%20for%20sale%20due%20to%20negligence%20of%20officials.%20Weeks%20after%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20was%20imposed%2C%20officials%20failed%20to%20erase%20PM's%20face%20on%20packets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffertiliser-shortage-in-madhya-pradesh-despite-abundant-stock-heres-why-4563396%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffertiliser-shortage-in-madhya-pradesh-despite-abundant-stock-heres-why-4563396%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffertiliser-shortage-in-madhya-pradesh-despite-abundant-stock-heres-why-4563396%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22THDCIL%20inks%20pacts%20to%20develop%203%2C270%20MW%20renewable%20energy%20projects%20in%20K'taka%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699601608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsm