VkCTm%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FSX3L7VkCTm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Alvin%20(%40sondesix)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsondesix%2Fstatus%2F1707780279979704444%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2029%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnushka%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20are%20quite%20particular%20about%20their%20private%20life.%20The%20couple%20got%20married%20in%20an%20intimate%20ceremony%20in%20Italy%20after%20dating%20for%20many%20years.%20They%20welcomed%20their%20daughter%20Vamika%20in%20January%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20talked%20about%20how%20Anushka%20Sharma's%20motherhood%20journey%20has%20inspired%20him.%20The%20cricketer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fvirat-kohli-calls-anushka-his-inspiration-opens-about-sacrifices-she-made-as-a-mom-3823325%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20gotten%20a%20lot%20of%20inspiration%20from%20home.%20We%20have%20had%20a%20child.%20It%20has%20been%20an%20unbelievably%20life-changing%20and%20transforming%20process%2C%20for%20parents%20yes%20but%20for%20a%20mother%20especially.%20For%20a%20mother%2C%20it's%20life-changing%20completely.%20And%20how%20she%20has%20been%20so%20strong%20through%20it%20and%20how%20she%20has%20been%20able%20to%20take%20all%20the%20challenges%20that%20have%20come%20her%20way.%20And%20I%20have%20seen%20everything.%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20transformation%20happen.%20That%20gave%20me%20so%20much%20strength%20and%20inspiration%20to%20say%20what%20I%20am%20experiencing%20is%20not%20even%205%20per%20cent%20of%20what%20she%20has%20gone%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202019%2C%20during%20one%20of%20her%20interviews%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fanushka-sharma-says-crude-pregnancy-rumours-could-keep-filmmakers-away-but-hasnt-happened-to-her-yet-2078014%5C%22%3EFilmfare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Anushka%20Sharma%20talked%20about%20how%20rumours%20of%20pregnancy%20could%20keep%20filmmakers%20away.%20Anushka%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI'm%20fortunate%20this%20has%20not%20happened.%20It%20could%20happen.%20An%20actress%20gets%20married%20and%20the%20next%20thing%20they%20talk%20about%20is%2C%20'Is%20she%20pregnant%3F'%20When%20she's%20dating%20it's%20like%2C%20'Shaadi%20karne%20wale%20hai%20ki%20nahi%3F'%20It's%20crude.%20You%20should%20allow%20people%20to%20live%20their%20life.%20What's%20the%20need%20to%20jump%20the%20gun%3F%20Then%20put%20someone%20in%20a%20position%20where%20they%20end%20up%20clarifying%20unnecessarily.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnushka%20Sharma%20will%20be%20next%20seen%20in%20the%20sports%20biopic%3Ci%3E%20Chakda%20Xpress.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699600440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F5phj8os8_virat-_625x300_10_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshe-is-pregnant-virat-kohli-and-anushka-s-viral-video-has-fans-excited-4563142%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20video%20was%20shared%20by%20Anushka%20Sharma's%20fan%20page%20on%20Instagram%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshe-is-pregnant-virat-kohli-and-anushka-s-viral-video-has-fans-excited-4563142%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshe-is-pregnant-virat-kohli-and-anushka-s-viral-video-has-fans-excited-4563142%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshe-is-pregnant-virat-kohli-and-anushka-s-viral-video-has-fans-excited-4563142%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Goodbye%2C%20Range%20Anxiety!%20Now%20Convert%20Your%20Petrol%20Two-Wheeler%20Into%20a%20Hybrid%20EV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20concept%20of%20sustainability%20gaining%20popularity%20and%20people%20increasingly%20interested%20in%20making%20eco-friendly%20choices%20to%20reduce%20their%20carbon%20footprint%2C%20India%20has%20witnessed%20a%20surge%20in%20innovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20finding%20alternatives%20to%20single-use%20plastics%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F97000%2Fansoo-gupta-one-shoe-trust-responsible-tourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresponsible%20tourism%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%20is%20experiencing%20a%20wave%20of%20cost-effective%20innovations%20in%20nearly%20every%20sector.%20Within%20the%20automobile%20industry%2C%20companies%20have%20introduced%20innovations%20in%20Electric%20Vehicles%20(EVs)%3B%20however%2C%20many%20consumers%20still%20express%20concerns%20over%20its%20battery%20life%2C%20with%20lingering%20anxiety%20about%20reaching%20a%20charging%20point%20or%20their%20destination%20before%20it%20runs%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20Green%20Tiger%20Mobility%20employs%20a%20unique%20model%20which%20enables%20you%20to%20seamlessly%20transition%20between%20petrol%20and%20electric%20power%20within%20the%20same%20vehicle.%20To%20put%20it%20simply%2C%20the%20company%20converts%20your%20conventional%20petrol%20vehicle%20into%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20operate%20on%20both%20petrol%20and%20electric%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20your%20battery%20running%20out%20mid-journey%3B%20you%20can%20easily%20switch%20to%20petrol.%20As%20the%20founder%2C%20Ashish%20Dokania%2C%20aptly%20puts%20it%20for%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20having%20two%20scooters%20in%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20to%20green%20mobility%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Ashish%20Donkaia%