s%20up%20to%20125cc.%C2%A0%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Ashish%20Dokania%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pursued%20an%20MBA%20in%20Gurugram%20and%20started%20his%20career%20in%20the%20banking%20sector.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20working%20with%20the%20bank%2C%20I%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20project%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F254648%2Fbengaluru-credr-electric-ev-startup-second-hand-petrol-scooter-new-ebike-two-wheeler-ather-exchange-honda-activa-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancing%20transactions%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eincluding%20a%20lot%20of%20infrastructure%20projects%20which%20kind%20of%20exposed%20me%20to%20renewable%20energy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202015%2C%20he%20joined%20another%20firm%20which%20worked%20along%20similar%20lines%20of%20renewable%20energy%20and%20solar%20energy.%20Working%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20sector%20for%20several%20years%20is%20what%20became%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20he%20perceived%20the%20idea%20of%20Green%20Tiger%20Mobility%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20long%20list%20of%20existing%20innovations%20like%20%E2%80%98battery%20swap%E2%80%99%20and%20longer%20range%20in%20two-wheeler%20EVs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20realised%20working%20in%20the%20sector%20was%20that%20with%20renewable%20energies%20that%20are%20dependent%20on%20nature%2C%20you%20cannot%20predict%20it%20as%20per%20your%20demand.%20In%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20now%20moving%20towards%20EVs%2C%20there%20will%20soon%20be%20a%20huge%20gap%20in%20demand%20and%20supply%20of%20renewable%20electricity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20line%20of%20thought%20prompted%20me%20to%20consider%20a%20solution%20similar%20to%20the%20setup%20we%20employ%20in%20our%20homes%2C%20with%20electricity%20as%20the%20primary%20source%20and%2