%20situated%20on%20the%20left-hand%20side%20at%20the%20rear%2C%20making%20the%20scooter%20inherently%20unbalanced%20and%20tilted%20towards%20the%20left.%20What%20our%20innovation%20involves%20is%20relocating%20the%20entire%20electric%20powertrain%20to%20the%20right%20side%20of%20the%20vehicle.%20This%20adjustment%20effectively%20rebalances%20the%20scooter%2C%20offering%20a%20more%20stable%20and%20balanced%20ride%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20a%20controller%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F283991%2Fnoise-top-smartwatch-brand-india-gaurav-amit-khatri-bikaner-success-startup-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmart%20display%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20indicates%20the%20amount%20of%20battery%20left%20and%20which%20mode%20the%20vehicle%20is%20running%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20indicates%20if%20there%20is%20any%20fault%20in%20the%20system%20or%20if%20there%20is%20a%20heating%20problem%20while%20the%20vehicle%20is%20running%20on%20electric%20mode%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dual%20powertrain%20mode%20or%20the%20retrofits%20are%20great%20not%20just%20because%20they%20are%20eco-friendly%20but%20it%20also%20reduces%20the%20anxiety%20of%20the%20rider%20over%20its%20range.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20a%20typical%20rider%20only%20uses%20their%20scooter%20for%20a%20range%20of%2050%20to%2060%20km.%20It%20is%20only%2C%20let%20us%20say%2C%20once%20a%20month%20that%20they%20might%20need%20to%20use%20it%20for%20another%20100%20or%20200%20km.%20So%20instead%20of%20giving%20the%20consumer%20more%20range%20or%20battery%20swap%2C%20what%20we%20gave%20them%20is%20a%20reliable%20petrol%20engine%20that%20will%20cover%20any%20extra%20distance%20that%20you%20want%20to%20travel%20on%20a%20given%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20method%