-highest-ever-sales-in-october-siam-123111000313_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20domestic%20sales%20for%20all%20vehicles%20in%20India%20were%20up%2020%25%20to%202%2C314%2C197%20units%20in%20October%20this%20year%20as%20compared%20to%201%2C923%2C721%20units%20last%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fpassenger-vehicles-3-wheelers-report-highest-ever-sales-in-october-siam-123111000313_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gang%20Behind%20Cyberattack%20On%20World's%20Biggest%20Bank%20Has%20Hacked%201%2C000%20Victims%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20trades%20handled%20by%20the%20world's%20largest%20bank%20in%20the%20globe's%20biggest%20market%20traversed%20Manhattan%20on%20a%20USB%20stick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndustrial%20%26amp%3B%20Commercial%20Bank%20of%20China%20Ltd.'s%20US%20unit%20had%20been%20hit%20by%20a%20cyberattack%2C%20rendering%20it%20unable%20to%20clear%20swathes%20of%20US%20Treasury%20trades%20after%20entities%20responsible%20for%20settling%20the%20transactions%20swiftly%20disconnected%20from%20the%20stricken%20systems.%20That%20forced%20ICBC%20to%20send%20the%20required%20settlement%20details%20to%20those%20parties%20by%20a%20messenger%20carrying%20a%20thumb%20drive%20as%20the%20state-owned%20lender%20raced%20to%20limit%20the%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workaround%20-%20described%20by%20market%20participants%20-%20followed%20the%20attack%20by%20suspected%20perpetrator%20Lockbit%2C%20a%20prolific%20criminal%20gang%20with%20ties%20to%20Russia%20that%20has%20also%20been%20linked%20to%20hits%20on%20Boeing%20Co.%2C%20ION%20Trading%20UK%20and%20the%20UK's%20Royal%20Mail.%20The%20strike%20caused%20immediate%20disruption%20as%20market-makers%2C%20brokerages%20and%20banks%20were%20forced%20to%20reroute%20trades%2C%20with%20many%20uncertain%20when%20access%20would%20resume.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20spotlights%20a%20danger%20that%20bank%20leaders%20concede%20keeps%20them%20up%20at%20night%20-%20the%20prospect%20of%20a%20cyberattack%20that%20could%20someday%20cripple%20a%20key%20piece%20of%20the%20financial%20system's%20wiring%2C%20setting%20off%20a%20cascade%20of%20disruptions.%20Even%20brief%20episodes%20prompt%20bank%20leaders%20and%20their%20government%20overseers%20to%20call%20for%20more%20vigilance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20true%20shock%20to%20large%20banks%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marcus%20Murray%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Swedish%20cybersecurity%20firm%20Truesec.%20%26quot%3BThe%20ICBC%20hack%20will%20make%20large%20banks%20around%20the%20globe%20race%20to%20improve%20their%20defenses%2C%20starting%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20details%20of%20the%20attack%20emerged%2C%20employees%20at%20the%20bank's%20Beijing%20headquarters%20held%20urgent%20meetings%20with%20the%20lender's%20US%20division%20and%20notified%20regulators%20as%20they%20discussed%20next%20steps%20and%20assessed%20the%20impact%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%20ICBC%20is%20considering%20seeking%20help%20from%20China's%20Ministry%20of%20State%20Security%20in%20light%20of%20the%20risks%20of%20potential%20attack%20on%20other%20units%2C%20the%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20Thursday%2C%20the%20bank%20confirmed%20it%20had%20experienced%20a%20ransomware%20attack%20a%20day%20earlier%20that%20disrupted%20some%20systems%20at%20its%20ICBC%20Financial%20Services%20unit.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20isolated%20the%20affected%20systems%20and%20that%20those%20at%20the%20bank's%20head%20office%20and%20other%20overseas%20units%20weren't%20impacted%2C%20nor%20was%20ICBC's%20New%20York%20branch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extent%20of%20the%20disruption%20wasn't%20immediately%20clear%2C%20though%20Treasury%20market%20participants%20reported%20liquidity%20was%20affected.%20The%20Securities%20Industry%20and%20Financial%20Markets%20Association%2C%20or%20Sifma%2C%20held%20calls%20with%20members%20about%20the%20matter%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICBC%20FS%20offers%20fixed-income%20clearing%2C%20Treasuries%20repo%20lending%20and%20some%20equities%20securities%20lending.%20The%20unit%20had%20%2423.5%20billion%20of%20assets%20at%20the%20end%20of%202022%2C%20according%20to%20its%20most%20recent%20annual%20filing%20with%20US%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20is%20only%20the%20latest%20to%20snarl%20parts%20of%20the%20global%20financial%20system.%20Eight%20months%20ago%2C%20ION%20Trading%20UK%20-%20a%20little-known%20company%20that%20serves%20derivatives%20traders%20worldwide%20-%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20ransomware%20attack%20that%20paralyzed%20markets%20and%20forced%20trading%20shops%20that%20clear%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20transactions%20a%20day%20to%20process%20deals%20manually.%20That%20has%20put%20financial%20institutions%20on%20high%20alert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICBC%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20lender%20by%20assets%2C%20has%20said%20it's%20been%20improving%20its%20cybersecurity%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20highlighting%20increased%20challenges%20from%20potential%20attacks%20amid%20the%20expansion%20of%20online%20transactions%2C%20adoption%20of%20new%20technologies%20and%20open%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bank%20actively%20responded%20to%20new%20challenges%20of%20financial%20cybersecurity%2C%20adhered%20to%20the%20bottom%20line%20for%20production%20safety%20and%20deepened%20the%20intelligent%20transformation%20of%20operation%20and%20maintenance%2C%26quot%3B%20ICBC%20said%20in%20its%20interim%20report%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERansomware%20attacks%20against%20Chinese%20firms%20appear%20rare%20in%20part%20because%20China%20has%20banned%20crypto-related%20transactions%2C%20according%20to%20Mattias%20Wahlen%2C%20a%20threat%20intelligence%20specialist%20at%20Truesec.%20That%20makes%20it%20harder%20for%20victims%20to%20pay%20ransom%2C%20which%20is%20often%20demanded%20in%20cryptocurrency%20because%20that%20form%20of%20payment%20provides%20more%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20latest%20attack%20likely%20exposes%20weaknesses%20in%20ICBC's%20defenses%2C%20Wahlen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20ICBC%20has%20had%20a%20less%20effective%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bpossibly%20because%20Chinese%20banks%20have%20not%20been%20tested%20as%20much%20as%20their%20Western%20counterparts%20in%20the%20past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecord%20Levels%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERansomware%20hackers%20have%20become%20so%20prolific%20that%20attacks%20may%20hit%20record%20levels%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlockchain%20analytics%20firm%20Chainalysis%20had%20recorded%20roughly%20%24500%20million%20of%20ransomware%20payments%20through%20the%20end%20of%20September%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20almost%2050%25%20from%20the%20same%20period%20a%20year%20earlier.%20Ransomware%20attacks%20surged%2095%25%20in%20the%20first%20three%20quarters%20of%20this%20year%2C%20compared%20with%20the%20same%20period%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20Corvus%20Insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20website%20of%20the%20New%20Zealand%20Stock%20Exchange%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20cyberattack%20that%20throttled%20traffic%20so%20severely%20that%20it%20couldn't%20post%20critical%20market%20announcements%2C%20forcing%20the%20entire%20operation%20to%20shut%20down.%20It%20was%20later%20revealed%20that%20more%20than%20100%20banks%2C%20exchanges%2C%20insurers%20and%20other%20financial%20firms%20worldwide%20were%20targets%20of%20the%20same%20type%20of%20so-called%20DDoS%20attacks%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaesars%20Entertainment%20Inc.%2C%20MGM%20Resorts%20International%20and%20Clorox%20Co.%20are%20among%20companies%20that%20have%20been%20hit%20by%20ransomware%20hackers%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICBC%20was%20struck%20as%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20works%20to%20reduce%20risks%20in%20the%20financial%20system%20with%20a%20raft%20of%20proposals%20that%20include%20mandating%20central%20clearing%20of%20all%20US%20Treasuries.%20Central%20clearing%20platforms%20are%20intermediaries%20between%20buyers%20and%20sellers%20that%20assume%20responsibility%20for%20completing%20transactions%20and%20therefore%20prevent%20a%20default%20of%20one%20counterparty%20from%20causing%20widespread%20problems%20in%20the%20marketplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20underscores%20the%20benefits%20of%20central%20clearing%20in%20the%20%2426%20trillion%20market%2C%20said%20Stanford%20University%20finance%20professor%20Darrell%20Duffie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20view%20it%20as%20one%20example%20of%20why%20central%20clearing%20in%20the%20US%20Treasuries%20market%20is%20a%20very%20good%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20had%20a%20similar%20problem%20occurred%20in%20a%20not-clearing%20firm%2C%20it's%20not%20clear%20how%20the%20default%20risk%20that%20might%20result%20would%20propagate%20through%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699597260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-11%2Fk7p6skds_hacking-generic-reuters_625x300_16_November_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flockbit-ransomware-behind-hacking-of-worlds-biggest-bank-a-gang-for-hire-4563169%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Industrial%20%26amp%3B%20Commercial%20Bank%20of%20China%20Ltd.'s%20US%20unit%20had%20been%20hit%20by%20a%20cyberattack%2C%20rendering%20it%20unable%20to%20clear%20swathes%20of%20US%20Treasury%20trades%20after%20entities%20responsible%20for%20settling%20the%20transactions%20swiftly%20disconnected%20from%20the%20stricken%20systems.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flockbit-ransomware-behind-hacking-of-worlds-biggest-bank-a-gan