k-on-one-of-the-chinas-largest-bank-icbc%2Farticleshow%2F105114619.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan's%20Smallest%20Booth%20Has%20Just%2035%20Voters%2C%20All%20Members%20Of%201%20Family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20five%20states%20are%20currently%20underway.%20While%20voting%20took%20place%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Mizoram%20on%20November%207%2C%20Rajasthan%20is%20due%20to%20vote%20on%20November%2025.%20Ahead%20of%20this%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20has%20set%20up%20a%20polling%20booth%20in%20a%20remote%20village%20on%20the%20Indo-Pak%20border%20in%20Barmer%20district%2C%20which%20has%20a%20population%20of%2035.%20And%20all%20these%20people%20are%20members%20of%20a%20single%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%2C%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3EBadmer%20Ka%20Paar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20faced%20a%20significant%20challenge%20during%20the%20election%20period%2C%20as%20people%20here%20had%20to%20travel%20a%20distance%20of%2020%20kilometres%20to%20the%20nearest%20polling%20station%20to%20cast%20their%20votes.%20This%20hard%20journey%20required%20walking%20or%20riding%20camels%2C%20making%20it%20particularly%20challenging%20for%20women%20and%20elderly%20people%20to%20undertake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fri2tfkgo_badmer-ka-paar_625x300_10_November_23.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20in%20previous%20elections%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20votes%20were%20cast%20by%20male%20members%20only.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20year%2C%20the%20fortunes%20have%20changed%2C%20and%20ECI's%20unique%20decision%20will%20benefit%20all%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20of%20the%20polling%