orts%20claiming%20that%20they%20were%20accused%20and%20found%20guilty%20of%20espionage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Qatari%20Court%20of%20First%20Instance%20handed%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fqatar-eight-former-indian-navy-officers-handed-death-penalty%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNew%2520Delhi%253A%2520The%2520eight%2520former%2Cit%2520was%2520%25E2%2580%259Cdeeply%2520shocked%25E2%2580%259D.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edeath%20sentence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20eight%20Indian%20nationals%20on%20October%2026%2C%20which%20the%20Indian%20government%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Cextremely%20shocking%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20weekly%20media%20briefing%2C%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%20that%20the%20copy%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cjudgment%20is%20confidential%20and%20has%20only%20been%20shared%20with%20the%20legal%20team%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20now%20pursuing%20further%20legal%20steps%2C%20and%20an%20appeal%20has%20been%20filed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stated%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20also%20remain%20engaged%20with%20the%20Qatari%20authorities%20on%20this%20matter%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20informed%20that%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20was%20granted%20consular%20access%20to%20them%20on%20November%207.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20family%20members%20too%2C%20and%20%5Bexternal%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%5D%20met%20them%20earlier%20this%20month%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20extend%20all%20legal%20and%20consular%20assistance.%20I%20would%20urge%20everyone%20not%20to%20engage%20in%20speculation%20considering%20the%20sensitive%20nature%20of%20the%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bagchi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20family%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20veterans%20had%20met%20with%20Jaishankar%20recently%2C%20who%20promised%20to%20give%20all%20possible%20support.%20The%20principal%20opposition%20party%20Congress%20had%20called%20on%20the%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fleverage-diplomatic-and-political-might-congress-to-centre-on-death-sentence-to-8-indians-in-qatar-2743486%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNew%2520Delhi%253A%2520With%2520eight%2520former%2Cutmost%2520to%2520get%2520them%2520released.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Euse%20its%20diplomatic%20and%20political%20leverage%20with%20the%20Qatar%20government%20to%20the%20maximum%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699592459000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F17100311%2FScreenshot-2023-03-17-at-10.02.44-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fappeal-lodged-death-sentence-navy-veterans-qatar-mea%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20weekly%20media%20briefing%2C%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%20that%20the%20copy%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cjudgment%20is%20confidential%20and%20has%20only%20been%20shared%20with%20the%20legal%20team%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fappeal-lodged-death-sentence-navy-veterans-qatar-mea%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australia%20offers%20climate%20refuge%20to%20Tuvalu%20citizens%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699592014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F54F1%2Fproduction%2F_112154712_breaking.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-67340907%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tuvalu%20-%20a%20series%20of%20low-lying%20atolls%20-%20is%20one%20of%20the%20countries%20most%20at%20risk%20from%20climate%20change.%22%2C%22author