gagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Anatomy%20of%20an%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine%3A%20What%20We%20Know%20and%26nbsp%3BWhat%20We%20Don%E2%80%99t%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09194755%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.39.03%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20September%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-pil-seeking-independent-audit-of-evm-source-codes-238408%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Erefused%20to%20entertain%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20asked%20for%20an%20audit%20of%20the%20source%20code%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20by%20an%20independent%20agency.%20While%20dismissing%20the%20case%2C%20the%20court%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20no%20material%20on%20record%20to%20indicate%20the%20Election%20Commission%20is%20not%20fulfilling%20its%20mandate.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20jury%20is%20still%20out%20on%20whether%20the%20ECI%20is%20following%20its%20mandate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20order%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20actual%20mechanics%20of%20that%20mandate%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%2C%20over%20the%20past%20month%2C%20analysed%20several%20publicly%20available%20documents%20and%20open%20sources%20of%20information%20on%20the%20machinery%20behind%20both%20the%20election%20process%20and%20the%20actual%20casting%20of%20ballots%2C%20i.e.%20the%20hardware%2C%20the%20software%20and%20the%20source%20code%20of%20EVMs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20entire%20election%20machinery%2C%20we%20found%2C%20from%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20EVMs%20to%20the%20software%20loaded%20on%20to%20them%2C%20to%20the%20committee%20appointed%20to%20evaluate%20the%20software%2C%20the%20so-called%20third-party%20auditing%20this%20software%20and%20much%20more%2C%20is%20controlled%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20ECI%20has%20very%20little%20say.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20holds%20true%20for%20the%20pre-election%20security%20measures%20put%20in%20place%20for%20the%20machines%2C%20such%20as%20first-level%20checking%20before%20they%20are%20sealed%20in%20a%20warehouse%20with%2024%C3%977%20security.%20Or%20the%20random%20allocation%20of%20the%20machines%20to%20constituencies.%20No%20officer%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20is%20present%20during%20any%20of%20these%20exercises.%20Instead%2C%20only%20officials%20of%20the%20two%20manufacturers%20are%20present%2C%20as%20is%20the%20district%20collector.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20does%20not%20have%20a%20say%20in%20the%20allocation%20of%20machines%20to%20a%20state%2C%20an%20exercise%20entrusted%20once%20again%20to%20the%20two%20PSUs.%20The%20ECI%2C%20however%2C%20can%20track%20the%20location%20of%20the%20machines%20using%20the%20EVM%20Tracking%20Software.%20It%20is%20only%20at%20the%20second%20%E2%80%9Crandomisation%E2%80%9D%20onwards%20that%20an%20election%20observer%20from%20Nirvachan%20Sadan%20is%20deputed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20%E2%80%98source%20code%E2%80%99%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20source%20code%20is%20a%20set%20of%20instructions%20in%20human%20readable%20language%20written%20by%20programmers.%20It%20provides%20the%20foundation%20for%20software%20and%20programme%20creation%20or%20basically%20everything%20that%20the%20machine%20does.%20The%20source%20code%20tells%20the%20machine%20how%20to%20function.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20petitioner%E2%80%99s%20contention%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20that%20the%20source%20code%2C%20or%20the%20brain%20of%20the%20machine%2C%20can%2C%20if%20altered%2C%20change%20the%20outcome%20of%20an%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EData%20gathered%20from%20open%20sources%20and%20Right%20to%20Information%20responses%20indicate%20that%20the%20source%20code%20of%20the%20EVMs%20has%20never%20been%20audited%2C%20let%20alone%20revealed%2C%20either%20by%20the%20ECI%2C%20the%20manufacturers%20or%20even%20the%20experts%20appointed%20to%20audit%20it%2C%20the%20Technical%20Evaluation%20Committees%20(TECs)%20mandated%20by%20the%20ECI%20to%20audit%20EVM%20software.%20They%20have%20never%20been%20given%20the%20source%20code.%20Manned%20by%20professors%20from%20the%20premier%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Technology%2C%20all%20members%20are%20appointed%20by%20the%20government.%20The%20ECI%20has%20no%20role.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESo%20how%20do%20the%20TECs%20carry%20out%20evaluations%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20go%20by%20what%20engineers%20working%20for%20the%20manufacturers%20say.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20crucial%20job%20of%20designing%20the%20source%20code%20and%20writing%20the%20software%20is%20carried%20out%20by%20a%20group%20of%20handpicked%20employees%20of%20the%20two%20public%20sector%20enterprises%2C%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Limited%20and%20Electronics%20Corporation%20of%20India%20Limited%20which%20also%20manufacture%20the%20EVMs.%20Both%20the%20PSUs%20are%20not%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20ECI.%20BEL%20is%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20and%20ECIL%20reports%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20story%20of%20EVMs%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20software%20of%20EVMs%20is%20developed%20in%20house%20by%20a%20selected%20group%20of%20engineers%20at%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20independently%20from%20each%20other.%20This%20select%20software%20development%20group%20of%20few%20engineers%20design%20and%20develop%20the%20source%20code%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20Status%20Paper%20on%20EVMs.%20This%20software%20is%20tested%20by%20another%20set%20of%20employees%20in%20house%20before%20the%20TEC%20vets%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F15684542%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F15684542%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F15684542%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20technical%20advice%20is%20given%20by%20the%20TEC.%20The%20Status%20Paper%20on%20EVMs%20does%20not%20spell%20out%20if%20the%20source%20code%20is%20shared%20with%20the%20TEC.%20It%20simply%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEntire%20software%20is%20vetted%20by%20the%20TEC%20and%20sealed%20by%20them.%20Golden%20copy%20%5Bthe%20original%20copy%2C%20which%20is%20meaningless%20unless%20one%20knows%20the%20code%20for%20writing%20the%20copy%5D%20remains%20under%20sealed%20condition%20only.%20This%20ensures%20that%20the%20software%20has%20really%20been%20written%20as%20per%20the%20requirements%20laid%20down%20for%20its%20intended%20use%20only.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20does%20not%20even%20have%20access%20to%20the%20software%20that%20is%20loaded%20onto%20the%20EVMs.%20That%20right%20rests%20solely%20with%20the%20manufacturer%20and%20technical%20experts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20IIT%20Delhi%20professor%2C%20Subhashis%20Banerjee%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20thought%20process%20is%20amateurish%20and%20language%20like%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20copy%E2%80%9D%20is%20non-standard.%20The%20whole%20approach%20reflects%20a%20lack%20of%20understanding%20of%20computer%20security%20and%20threat%20models.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSource%20code%2C%E2%80%9D%20clarifies%20Banerjee%2C%20is%20the%20computer%20programme%20that%20runs%20in%20a%20computing%20device.%20It%20is%20a%20high-level%20representation%20programmed%20by%20developers%20which%20gets%20translated%20to%20a%20machine%20form%20(by%20a%20process%20called%20compiling)%20and%20executes%20on%20the%20CPU.%20Source%20code%20is%20the%20original%20version.%20In%20general%2C%20there%20is%20no%20way%20to%20establish%20that%20the%20programme%20that%20runs%20in%20a%20computer%20indeed%20corresponds%20to%20a%20given%20source%20code.%20Establishing%20it%20for%20multiple%20EVMs%20is%20an%20impossibility.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20there%20is%20not%20trojan%20or%20malware%20cannot%20be%20determined%20by%20%E2%80%9Ccode%20in%20the%20EVM%20units%20can%20be%20read%20out%20by%20an%20approved%20external%20unit%20and%20the%20code%20so%20read%20may%20be%20compared%20with%20corresponding%20reference%20code%20to%20show%20that%20code%20is%20same%20as%20that%20in%20the%20reference%20units.%20The%20scope%20of%20comparison%20is%20only%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20trojan%20or%20other%20malware%20for%20EVMs%20in%20use.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUp%20until%202010%2C%20no%20one%20from%20the%20government%2C%20be%20it%20the%20ECI%2C%20the%20TEC%2C%20the%20manufacturers%20or%20third%20party%2C%20could%20actually%20extract%20the%20source%20code%20from%20the%20chips%20embedded%20in%20the%20machines.%20The%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20Status%20Paper%20on%20EVMs%2C%20Edition%204%2C%20of%20November%202021%20clearly%20says%20the%20%E2%80%9Cexact%20original%20source%20code%20cannot%20be%20derived%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20older%20versions%20of%20EVMs%20(M1%20and%20M2)%20manufactured%20till%202010.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20chips%20or%20micro%20controllers%20were%20imported%20and%20came%20pre-loaded.%20Any%20attempt%20to%20tinker%20with%20the%20hardware%20would%20make%20these%20one-time%20programmable%20chips%20redundant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09193848%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.38.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22871%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09193848%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.38.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup.png%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09193848%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.38.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup-300x120.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684359%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22347%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWay%20back%20in%201990%20when%20the%20first%20evaluation%20was%20done%2C%20the%20TEC%20had%20recommended%20that%20source%20codes%20be%20made%20public.%20The%20TEC%20report%20of%201990%20accessed%20under%20RTI%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20matter%20of%20abundant%20precaution%2C%20the%20instrument%E2%80%99s%20signature%20may%20be%20tested%20by%20the%20suppliers%20before%20a%20poll%20to%20check%20that%20they%20have%20not%20been%20replaced.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20repeated%20by%20the%202006%20committee%20as%20well%2C%20which%20did%20not%20have%20access%20to%20the%20code%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20TEC%20in%20fact%20recommended%20again%20and%20again%20that%20the%20veil%20of%20secrecy%20surrounding%20source%20codes%20should%20be%20lifted.%20In%202013%2C%20the%20TEC%20said%20that%20a%20facility%20be%20provided%20so%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccode%20in%20the%20EVM%20units%20can%20be%20read%20out%20by%20an%20approved%20external%20unit%20and%20the%20code%20so%20read%20may%20be%20compared%20with%20corresponding%20reference%20code%20to%20show%20that%20code%20is%20same%20as%20that%20in%20the%20reference%20units.%20The%20scope%20of%20comparision%20is%20only%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20trojan%20or%20other%20malware%20for%20EVMs%20in%20use.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20report%20of%202013%20was%20the%20last%20the%20government%20shared%20with%20activist%20Venkatesh%20Nayak%20via%20RTI.%20No%20report%20has%20been%20made%20public%20post%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09202231%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-8.22.09%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09202231%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-8.22.09%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09202231%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-8.22.09%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x227.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09202231%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-8.22.09%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x773.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684375%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22906%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EScreenshots%20of%20the%20TEC%20recommendation%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENayak%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20officials%20are%20present%20at%20any%20stage%20be%20it%20manufacturing%20or%20software%20development%20or%20testing.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20they%20even%20see%20the%20machines%20before%20they%20reach%20the%20warehouses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EToo%20much%20secrecy%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20disproportionate%20secrecy%20is%20in%20marked%20contrast%20to%20other%20countries%20still%20using%20electronic%20voting%20devices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAustralian%20EVMs%20use%20Linux%2C%20an%20open-source%20software.%20Venezuela%20audits%20its%20source%20code%20before%20every%20election.%20The%20US%20keeps%20its%20source%20codes%20and%20hashes%20in%20a%20public%20repository%20and%20Germany%20and%20several%20other%20countries%20have%20got%20rid%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machines.%20In%20India%2C%20votaries%20of%20those%20fighting%20for%20transparency%20say%20if%20the%20secrecy%20surrounding%20source%20codes%20is%20lifted%2C%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20for%20insiders%20to%20maliciously%20manipulate%20the%20software.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEmails%20and%20phone%20calls%20to%20officials%20of%20the%20ECI%20and%20spokesperson%20elicited%20no%20response.%20However%2C%20government%20officials%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20reason%20why%20the%20source%20code%20information%20should%20be%20shared.%20People%20have%20gone%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20again%20and%20again%20on%20this%20matter%20and%20their%20efforts%20have%20been%20rebuffed.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20has%20answered%20the%20court%20each%20time.%20These%20are%20nothing%20but%20motivated%20questions.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20CEC%2C%20Ashok%20Lavasa%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20a%20number%20of%20discussions%20on%20making%20source%20code%20public%20though%20the%20ECI%20goes%20by%20what%20the%20TEC%20says.%20The%20ECI%20prefers%20to%20be%20guided%20by%20academics%20like%20those%20at%20the%20TEC%20and%20go%20with%20their%20wisdom.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELavasa%20says%20the%20system%20should%20be%20foolproof%20and%20the%20intent%20should%20be%20to%20have%20a%20robust%20system%20in%20place.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20suggestions%20on%20counting%20all%20VVPAT%20slips%20even%20though%20this%20will%20be%20time%20consuming.%20However%2C%20trust%20and%20not%20speed%20should%20be%20of%20the%20essence.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20ECI%20to%20satisfy%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20doubts%20by%20introducing%20a%20modicum%20of%20credibility%2C%20dialogue%20and%20transparency%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09195651%2FUntitled-design-10.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09195651%2FUntitled-design-10.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09195651%2FUntitled-design-10-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09195651%2FUntitled-design-10-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684366%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20GODL-India%20%26lt%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fdata.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FGazette_Notification_OGDL.pdf%3E%2C%20via%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20petitioner%20Sunil%20Ahya%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20access%20the%20source%20code%20since%202018%20under%20RTI.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commissioner%20nudged%20the%20competent%20authority%20(the%20ECI)%20to%20examine%20if%20the%20source%20code%20details%20could%20be%20made%20public%20especially%20since%20this%20will%20create%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20trust%20in%20the%20voting%20system%E2%80%9D.%20The%20ECI%20stand%20was%20source%20codes%20are%20%E2%80%9Cintellectual%20property%20rights%E2%80%9D.%20It%20has%20not%20responded%20to%20the%20CIC%20suggestion%20till%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20default%20mode%20has%20been%20opacity%2C%20including%20the%20response%20given%20to%20RTIs%20submitted%20to%20them.%20In%202019%2C%20Ahya%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20since%20the%20ECI%20would%20not%20share%20the%20source%20code%20with%20him.%20When%20the%20petition%20came%20up%20before%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Ranjan%20Gogoi%2C%20the%20ECI%20told%20the%20court%20that%20a%20TEC%20of%20the%20ECI%20audits%20the%20software%20and%20any%20information%20is%20available%20with%20the%20TEC.%20But%20the%20TEC%20told%20Ahya%20and%20Nayak%20in%20separate%20RTI%20replies%20that%20audit%20is%20done%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%E2%80%99s%20(MEITY%E2%80%99s)%20audit%20cell%2C%20called%20the%20Standardisation%20Testing%20and%20Quality%20Certification%20(STQC).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESTQC%20in%20turn%20said%20this%20information%20is%20with%20the%20ECI.%20The%20RTI%20was%20transferred%20by%20STQC%20to%20the%20ECI%20under%20Rule%206%20(3)%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%2C%20which%20says%20that%20if%20information%20is%20not%20available%20with%20a%20particular%20arm%20of%20the%20government%2C%20the%20appeal%20should%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20one%20that%20has%20the%20information.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20EVM%20status%20paper%20explains%20the%20role%20of%20the%20STQC%20as%2C%20%E2%80%9CSTQC%20tests%20and%20clears%20the%20EVMs%20before%20these%20are%20shipped%20out%20from%20BEL%2FECIL%E2%80%9D.%20The%20ECI%20status%20paper%20simply%20calls%20STQC%20%E2%80%9Ca%20third%20party%20testing%20agency%E2%80%9D%20without%20mentioning%20its%20parent%20body%2C%20MEITY.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EInside%20an%20EVM%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20only%20time%20when%20an%20EVM%20was%20officially%20opened%20and%20its%20mechanics%20examined%20was%20under%20orders%20of%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20in%20May%202017.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20plea%20regarding%20an%20alleged%20vote%20mismatch%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%202014%20assembly%20poll%20filed%20by%20Congress%20candidate%20Abhay%20Chhajed%20from%20Pune%E2%80%99s%20Parvathi%20constituency.%20The%20Central%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%2C%20Hyderabad%20was%20asked%20to%20examine%2C%20amongst%20other%20things%2C%20if%20the%20source%20code%20has%20been%20tampered%20with%20and%20if%20the%20hash%20values%20of%20these%20source%20codes%20were%20the%20same%20or%20different.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChhajed%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20strange%20that%20when%20the%20machine%20reached%20CFSL%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20under%20Y%20plus%20security%20there%20were%20at%20least%2040%20people%20waiting%20for%20its%20arrival%2C%20right%20from%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%2C%20CID%20and%20other%20Intelligence%20agencies%20as%20well%20as%20state%20police%20and%20several%20others.%20There%20was%20so%20much%20paranoia.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CFSL%20gave%20a%20clean%20chit%20but%20not%20before%20admitting%20they%20did%20not%20have%20the%20technical%20expertise%20to%20examine%20the%20machine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09201854%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-8.14.33%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22616%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09201854%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-8.14.33%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%20616w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09201854%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-8.14.33%25E2%2580%25AFPM-191x300.png%20191w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684373%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22966%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Seeking%20additional%20time%2C%20the%20lab%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20analysis%20of%20the%20Exhibits%20pertaining%20to%20EVM%20appear%20to%20be%20complex%20in%20nature%20as%20such%20reference%20is%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20this%20laboratory%20which%20involves%20interaction%20with%20the%20concerned%20technologists%20and%20to%20understand%20the%20nature%20of%20functioning.%E2%80%9D%20The%20report%20when%20it%20came%2C%20was%20signed%20by%20a%20ballistic%20expert%20and%20by%20a%20scientist%20of%20physics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F683345418%2FEVM-CFSL-Report%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20EVM%20CFSL%20Report%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EEVM%20CFSL%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fuser%2F286754081%2FThe-Wire%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20The%20Wire's%20profile%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Scribd%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F683345418%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-Cmj88Pm8S2uYNJoZrdpo%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.75%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%20EVM%20CFSL%20Report%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20experts%20said%20the%20microprocessor%20or%20chip%20was%20One%20Time%20Programmable%2C%20meaning%20once%20the%20programme%20is%20written%20into%20it%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20modified.%20Or%20in%20other%20words%2C%20another%20software%20could%20not%20be%20written%20over%20it%20and%20it%20is%20therefore%20secure.%20The%20status%20paper%20echoes%20that%20position%3A%20%E2%80%9CEVM%20used%20by%20the%20commission%20is%20a%20standalone%20non%20networked%2C%20one-time%20programmable%20machine.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CFSL%20report%20does%20not%20give%20details%20on%20the%20make%20of%20the%20machine%20they%20examined.%20It%20is%20also%20unclear%20which%20make%20of%20machine%20was%20used%20in%20the%202014%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20poll%20but%20post%202013%2C%20it%20is%20the%20M3%20type%20that%20is%20being%20manufactured%20by%20ECIL%20and%20BEL.%20While%20the%20M1%20and%20M2%20machines%20manufactured%20up%20to%202010%20used%20OTP%20chips%2C%20the%20Status%20Paper%20on%20EVMs%20is%20silent%20about%20the%20technology%20used%20for%20the%20latest%20M3%20machine%20chips%20or%20micro%20controllers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09195651%2FUntitled-design-10.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09195651%2FUntitled-design-10.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09195651%2FUntitled-design-10-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09195651%2FUntitled-design-10-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684366%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20GODL-India%20%26lt%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fdata.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FGazette_Notification_OGDL.pdf%3E%2C%20via%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESoftware%20for%20EVMs%20at%20factory%20itself%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20EVM%20Status%20Paper%20says%20that%20software%20for%20the%20EVMs%20is%20written%20at%20the%20factory%20itself.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20software%20of%20the%20EVMs%20is%20developed%20in%20house%20by%20a%20selected%20group%20of%20engineers%20in%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20independently%20from%20each%20other.%20This%20select%20software%20development%20group%20of%20few%20engineers%20design%20and%20develop%20the%20source%20code.%20Technological%20advancements%20now%20permit%20the%20writing%20of%20the%20machine%20code%20into%20the%20chips%20at%20PSU%20premises%20itself.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EQuestions%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20TEC%20chief%20D.T.%20Sahani%20and%20member%20Rajat%20Moona.%20Sahani%20is%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20emails%20and%20phone%20calls.%20Moona%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20talk%20to%20Sahani%20as%20%E2%80%9Che%20is%20heading%20the%20TEC%E2%80%9D.%20The%20TEC%20was%20asked%20about%20how%20it%20evaluates%20the%20software%2C%20whether%20the%20source%20code%20has%20been%20ever%20shared%20with%20the%20committee%20and%20whether%20international%20standards%20are%20followed%20in%20auditing%20the%20source%20code.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20software%20is%20developed%20in-house%20by%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20and%20both%20PSUs%20are%20independent%20of%20each%20other%2C%20the%20ECI%20manual%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20means%20that%20half%20of%20the%20EVMs%20countrywide%20have%20one%20software%20and%20the%20other%20half%20have%20another.%20If%20the%20software%20is%20developed%20in-house%2C%20it%20means%20that%20it%20is%20either%20developed%20by%20employees%20of%20the%20PSU%20or%20it%20is%20outsourced%20to%20a%20third%20party.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20software%20for%20the%20EVMs%20is%20developed%20and%20written%20by%20government%20employees%20working%20for%20the%20two%20PSUs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESoftware%20chips%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20what%20about%20the%20chip%20or%20the%20microcontroller%20on%20which%20the%20unknown%20government%20employees%20write%20the%20software%3F%20There%20is%20no%20clarity%20on%20specific%20details%20here.%20The%20EVM%20status%20paper%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20absence%20of%20requisite%20facilities%20to%20produce%20micro-controllers%20in%20India%20micro%20controllers%20are%20procured%20from%20manufacturers%20abroad.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20chip%20used%20in%20the%20EVMs%20are%20imported%20by%20the%20two%20government-controlled%20PSUs%20but%20both%20are%20silent%20about%20which%20country%20or%20company%20they%20are%20importing%20EVM%20chips%20from.%20Repeated%20RTIs%20requests%20seeking%20this%20information%20have%20been%20rebuffed%20by%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F683344814%2FEVM-Chip-product-info%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20EVM%20Chip%20product%20info%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EEVM%20Chip%20product%20info%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fuser%2F286754081%2FThe-Wire%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20The%20Wire's%20profile%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Scribd%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F683344814%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-nHVNbDjKZ44p4PBD9uPe%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7729220222793488%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22EVM%20Chip%20product%20info%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20RTI%20response%20to%20Venkatesh%20Nayak%2C%20BEL%20admitted%20that%20the%20chip%20they%20are%20using%20is%20from%20US-based%20NXP%20semiconductors.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20NXP%20website%20says%2C%20this%20is%20not%20OTP.%20Instead%2C%20it%20has%20three%20different%20kinds%20of%20memory%20%E2%80%93%20SRAM%2C%20FLASH%20AND%20EEPROM.%20All%20three%20types%20can%20erase%20and%20rewrite%20data%2C%20or%20retain%20data%20bits%20in%20its%20memory%20or%20the%20memory%20can%20be%20electronically%20erased%20and%20rewritten.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20software%20that%20can%20be%20overwritten%20or%20reprogrammed%20cannot%20have%20the%20safeguards%20of%20being%20one%20time%20programmed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20paper%20on%20EVMs%20in%202010%2C%20a%20committee%20including%20Michigan%20University%20professor%20Alex%20J.%20Halderman%20had%20this%20to%20say%20with%20reference%20to%20expert%20committee%20members%20picked%20for%20EVMs%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20time%20the%20committee%20members%20were%20A.K.%20Agarwala%20and%20D.T.%20Shahani%2C%20with%20P.V.%20Indiresan%20serving%20as%20chair.%20All%20three%20were%20affiliated%20with%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20but%2C%20like%20the%20first%20committee%2C%20none%20appear%20to%20have%20had%20prior%20computer%20security%20expertise.%20Again%2C%20the%20committee%20members%20did%20not%20have%20access%20to%20EVM%20source%20code%20and%20relied%20on%20presentations%2C%20demonstrations%2C%20and%20site%20visits%20with%20the%20manufacturers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20their%20report%2C%20the%20ECI%20has%20reiterated%20its%20view%20that%20the%20machines%20were%20%E2%80%9Ctamper-proof%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Professor%20Indiresan%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20once%20said%20that%20questioning%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20integrity%20is%20like%20asking%20Sita%20to%20undergo%20trial%20by%20fire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699587000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09194755%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.39.03%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-anatomy-of-an-electronic-voting-machine-what-we-know-and-what-we-dont%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recent%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20asking%20for%20the%20source%20code%20of%C2%A0EVMs%20was%20dismissed.%20But%20there%20are%20important%20questions%20that%20remain%20about%20the%20code%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20making%20it%20public%20and%20other%20software%20deployed%20for%20the%20machines.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-anatomy-of-an-electronic-voting-machine-what-we-know-and-what-we-dont%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Divided%20communities%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699585570000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F17EA4%2Fproduction%2F_131665979_bethlehem1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67376148%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arabs%20and%20Jews%20living%20in%20the%20territory%20say%20the%207%20October%20attacks%20have%20deepened%20distrust.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67376148%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67376148.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%2