er%20conducted%20a%20total%20of%2060%20rolling%20landings%2C%20including%2010%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-35Bs%20were%20modified%20to%20carry%20testing%20sensors%20and%20were%20flown%20by%20US%20Marine%20pilots%20from%20a%20test%20and%20evaluation%20squadron%20assigned%20to%20Naval%20Air%20Station%20Patuxent%20River%20in%20Maryland.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dvidshub.net%2Fnews%2F456583%2Ff-35-test-team-hms-prince-wales-ships-company-working-closely-achieve-dt-3-goals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E200-strong%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Pax%20River's%20F-35%20Integrated%20Test%20Force%20also%20deployed%20onboard%20HMS%20Prince%20of%20Wales%20to%20support%20the%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22F-35B%20launch%20HMS%20Prince%20of%20Wales%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654cfb1b3cc84b4dfaff55d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20flight%20deck%20officer%20signals%20an%20F-35B%20to%20launch%20from%20HMS%20Prince%20of%20Wales.%3Cp%3ERoyal%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWestlant%202023%20is%20only%20the%20latest%20round%20of%20trials%20for%20the%20jet%20and%20the%20carriers.%20This%20deployment%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royalnavy.mod.uk%2Fnews-and-latest-activity%2Fnews%2F2023%2Fnovember%2F08%2F20231108-britains-biggest-warship-extends-the-boundaries-of-uk-carrier-operations%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocused%20on%3C%2Fa%3E%20expanding%20the%20capabilities%20of%20both%20of%20Britain's%20new%20carriers%2C%20especially%20their%20ability%20to%20launch%20and%20recover%20F-35s%20faster%2C%20in%20worse%20weather%2C%20and%20at%20day%20and%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20and%20British%20experts%20will%20now%20analyze%20the%20data%20gathered%20during%20the%20tests%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20the%20ship's%20command%20team%20are%20