0navigating%20the%20streets%20of%20Berkeley%2C%20California%20a%20hair-raising%20experience.%20Its%20towering%2C%20blocky%20hood%20%E2%80%94%20which%20came%20up%20to%20my%20chest%20%E2%80%94%20was%20a%20major%20impediment%20to%20forward%20visibility.%20I%20frequently%20feared%20that%20I%20was%20veering%20dangerously%20close%20to%20parked%20cars%20or%20to%20oncoming%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20fairly%20tall%20and%20spry%2C%20but%20getting%20the%20aforementioned%20bikes%20up%20and%20into%20the%20F-150's%20bed%20still%20necessitated%20using%20its%20extending%20tailgate%20step%20and%20handrail.%20When%20trucks%20start%20offering%20escalators%2C%20that's%20when%20you'll%20know%20size%20has%20really%20gotten%20out%20of%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bed%20of%20the%202023%20Ford%20F-150%20Lightning%20Platinum%2C%20with%20a%20built-in%20step%20engaged.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651b1ed3617692f0d03ce943%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202023%20Ford%20F-150%20Lightning%20Platinum.%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EPeople%20don't%20use%20trucks%20in%20the%20way%20you'd%20expect%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20pickup%20trucks%20are%20bigger%20and%20more%20popular%20than%20ever.%20What's%20especially%20odd%20is%20people%20don't%20even%20universally%20depend%20on%20them%20for%20truck%20stuff.%20Lots%20of%20owners%20just%20use%20them%20to%20tootle%20around%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20market%20research%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.strategicvision.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStrategic%20Vision%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2043%25%20of%20full-size%20truck%20buyers%20use%20their%20trucks%20daily%20to%20go%20to%20and%20from%20work%20and%2088%25%20use%20them%20as%20their%20primary%20vehicle%2C%20roughly%20matching%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20car%20market.%3C%2Fp%3