4%20will%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20launched%20Omegle%20as%20in%202009%2C%20then-18-year-old%20founder%20Leif%20K-Brooks%20saw%20the%20internet%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20village%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20long%20post%20Thursday.%20He%20said%20he%20wanted%20the%20site%20to%20be%20like%20%26quot%3Bstrolling%20down%20a%20street%20in%20that%20village%2C%20striking%20up%20conversations%20with%20the%20people%20you%20ran%20into%20along%20the%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20random%20connections%20sometimes%20turned%20dark.%20And%20the%20site%20is%20shutting%20down%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20an%202021%20lawsuit%20filed%20in%20Oregon%20that%20accused%20Omegle%20of%20matching%20a%20user%20who%20was%2011%20at%20the%20time%20with%20a%20sexual%20predator%2C%20the%20AP%20reported%2C%20citing%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fecf.ord.uscourts.gov%2Fcgi-bin%2FDktRpt.pl%3F977091799832986-L_1_0-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecords%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOmegle%20allowed%20users%20to%20randomly%20chat%20with%20strangers%20over%20text%20or%20video.%20They'd%20be%20matched%20randomly%20with%20someone%20in%20less%20than%20a%20minute%2C%20or%20they%20could%20choose%20to%20chat%20with%20someone%20who%20listed%20similar%20interest%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20instant%20success%2C%20K-Brooks%20said%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20served%20as%20the%20subject%20of%20viral%20YouTube%20videos%20during%20its%20heyday.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt%20also%20had%20a%20resurgence%20with%20isolated%20teens%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F07%2F24%2Fstyle%2Fomegle-random-video-chat.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222878%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emma%20Chamberlain%20on%20omegle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654d28e5b788914e55537bf4%3F