As%20Independent%2C%20Joins%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot's%20close%20aide%20and%20former%20Jodhpur%20mayor%20Rameshwar%20Dadhich%2C%20who%20had%20filed%20his%20nomination%20for%20the%20upcoming%20state%20Assembly%20polls%20from%20the%20Soorsagar%20constituency%20as%20an%20independent%20candidate%2C%20withdrew%20his%20papers%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Dausa%20district%20president%20of%20the%20Congress%20Vinod%20Sharma%20also%20joined%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20on%20Thursday.%20In%20Jaipur%2C%20former%20minister%20Rajpal%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20who%20had%20filed%20his%20papers%20from%20Jhotwara%20against%20the%20BJP's%20Rajyavardhan%20Singh%20Rathore%2C%20withdrew%20his%20nomination%20following%20talks%20with%20the%20party%20high-command.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20joined%20the%20BJP%20due%20to%20the%20decision-making%20capacity%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20I%20have%20been%20impressed%20with%20his%20work%20for%20long.%20If%20Modi%20was%20not%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20(in%20Ayodhya%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh)%20could%20not%20have%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dadhich%20said%20after%20joining%20the%20saffron%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Union%20minister%20and%20the%20party's%20Rajasthan%20election%20in-charge%20Pralhad%20Joshi%2C%20Union%20minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20and%20MP%20Rajendra%20Gehlot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shekhawat%20said%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20parties%20are%20joining%20the%20BJP%20as%20they%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20policies%20and%20fake%20promises%20of%20such%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20time%20has%20come%20for%20the%20departure%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20from%20the%20desert%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20BJP%20rebels%2C%20incl