y%2Faustralia-domestic-help-high-commissioner%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20reported%20earlier%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20implications%20of%20the%20judgment%20on%20diplomatic%20privileges%20and%20immunities%2C%20since%20the%20complainant%20Seema%20Shergill%20had%20been%20in%20Australia%20with%20an%20official%20passport%20with%20a%20diplomatic%20visa%20during%20the%20period%20of%20the%20dispute.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20first%20response%20from%20India%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%20that%20New%20Delhi%20%E2%80%9Creject%5Bs%5D%20any%20locus%20standi%20of%20Australian%20authorities%20to%20adjudicate%20on%20matters%20concerning%20such%20India-based%20Service%20Staff%20of%20the%20High%20Commission%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20India%20was%20%E2%80%9Ctaking%20up%20the%20matter%E2%80%9D%20with%20Australia%2C%20Bagchi%20urged%20Canberra%20%E2%80%9Cto%20uphold%20its%20obligations%20under%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations%2C%20particularly%20in%20relation%20to%20diplomatic%20immunities%20and%20privileges%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeema%20Shergill%20had%20travelled%20with%20Suri%20as%20India-based%20service%20staff%20in%202015.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20she%20left%20the%20official%20residence%2C%20known%20as%20India%20House%2C%20without%20information.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBagchi%20claimed%20that%20Shergill%20had%20%E2%80%9Cwillfully%20deserted%20her%20post%20in%20May%202016%2C%20a%20day%20before%20her%20scheduled%20return%20to%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20then%2C%20we%20have%20repeatedly%20requested%20Australian%20authorities%20to%20locate%20and%20repatriate%20her%20to%20India.%20We%20have%20learnt%20that%20she%20has%20made%20allegations%20against%20the%20t