vercoming%20all%20odds%2C%20using%20her%20disability%20as%20motivation%20to%20pursue%20her%20dream%2C%20in%20her%20own%20words.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOf%20closing%20the%20door%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98dark%20room%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20childhood%20and%20memories%2C%20most%20of%20my%20time%20was%20spent%20in%20my%20room%2C%20which%20felt%20darker%20with%20each%20passing%20day.%20Whereas%20my%20parents%20refused%20to%20give%20up%20on%20doctors%2C%20waiting%20for%20a%20miracle%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20my%20childhood%20was%20spent%20visiting%20various%20doctors%20and%20hospitals.%20A%20very%20tiring%20affair%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20as%20all%20those%20visits%20would%20lead%20us%20to%20nothing%20but%20dead%20ends.%20This%20whole%20ordeal%20made%20me%2C%20in%20a%20manner%20of%20speaking%2C%20%E2%80%98a%20sad%20child%E2%80%99.%20I%20would%20only%20stay%20in%20my%20room%20all%20day%20and%20spend%20my%20time%20staring%20at%20the%20ceiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBalalatha-2-1699451601.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Balalatha%20has%20taught%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20students%20so%20far%20and%20100%20of%20them%20were%20able%20to%20crack%20the%20exam.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBalalatha-2-1699451601.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBalalatha-2-1699451601-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBalalatha-2-1699451601-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBalalatha-2-1699451601-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia