2%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Findia%2Fhealth-topics%2Fsnakebite%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSnakebite%2520in%2520India%2C-The%2520World%2520Health%26amp%3Btext%3DPublished%2520reports%2520suggest%2520that%2520between%2Camputations%2520and%2520other%2520permanent%2520disabilities.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E90%20percent%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20snakebites%20are%20caused%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98big%20four%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Common%20krait%2C%20Indian%20cobra%2C%20Russell%E2%80%99s%20viper%2C%20and%20the%20Saw%20Scaled%20Viper.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20delay%20in%20administering%20the%20anti-snake%20venom%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20says%2C%20chances%20are%20the%20snake%20bite%20will%20cause%20grave%20organ%20damage%2C%20or%20prove%20to%20be%20fatal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20usually%20critically%20ill%20patients%20had%20to%20go%20to%20cities%20for%20treatment%20as%20there%20was%20no%20ambulance%20or%20support%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20many%20would%20die%20on%20their%20way%20to%20the%20hospital.%20Those%20who%20could%20not%20go%20to%20the%20city%20would%20visit%20faith%20healers%20and%20waste%20the%20golden%20hour%20for%20the%20treatment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20found%20that%20medical%20officers%20at%20the%20primary%20health%20centres%20would%20be%20reluctant%20to%20treat%20such%20cases%20as%20they%20either%20lacked%20antivenoms%20or%20necessary%20equipment%20such%20as%20ventilator%20support.%20They%20lack%20training%20to%20handle%20such%20emergency%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20started%20equipping%20his%20hospital%20with%20life%20saving%20equipment%20like%20cardiac%20monitors%2C%20ventilators%2C%20and%20oxygen%20cylinders%2C%20so%20that%20he%20could%20save%20lives%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20Over%20the%20past%2028%20years%2C%20his%20efforts%20have%20turned%20into%20a%20mission%20that%20aims%20at%20